  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091227" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">本发明涉及一种语音字典形成方法、语音识别系统及其方法。该系统包括顺序连接的语音输入模块、语音识别模块和输出模块、以及安装有语音字典的标准语音模块，语音识别模块和所述标准语音模块连接，其根据每个字或几个字的读音给出相应可供选择的文本，所述语音字典里的语音代码是通过存储日常生活中常会组合在一起使用的文字的标准读音而得到。本发明基于人们使用语言的习惯，把日常生活中常会组合在一起使用的文字的标准读音存储成语音字典安装在标准语音模块里，只要输入的语音符合语音字典里对应常用词或句的读音，就可以识别出输入的语音，转换成相应的文本，大大地提高向手持移动终端或计算机输入文本文字的速度。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091227" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The patent refers to the field of 'speech analysis or synthesis and speech recognition'. The invention refers to phonetic dictionary forming method, voice recognition system and method. The voice recognition system includes voice input module, voice recognition module and output module connected successively as well as standard voice module with phonetic dictionary. The phonetic dictionary has phonetic codes obtained through storing the standard pronunciations of common phrases. After inputting the standard pronunciation, the present invention can recognize the pronunciation and convert into corresponding text, and this can raise the text input speed in hand held terminal and computer greatly</p>
  </abstract>
